```{r setup, include=FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = FALSE)
library(plotly)
library(datasets)
```

## Plot: Chick Weights

```{r cars, echo = TRUE}
data <- as.data.frame(ChickWeight)
plot_ly(ChickWeight,
        x = ~Chick,
        y= ~weight,
        type = "scatter",
        mode = 'markers',
        color = ~Diet
        ,size = ~Time)
```
